OL,3,CWelsh Bible printed in 1588 to go on
OL,4,Cdisplay in Wales for first time
OL,6,FA rare copy of the first complete
OL,7,Ftranslation of the Bible into Welsh,
OL,8,Fprinted in 1588, will be displayed in
OL,9,FWales for the first time.
OL,11,FDescribed as being of exceptional
OL,12,Fhistorical significance, the 26cm book
OL,13,Fwill be available for the public to
OL,14,Fview at St Davids Cathedral in
OL,15,FPembrokeshire, after having been kept
OL,16,Fin Westminster Abbey's library
OL,17,Fcollection.
