OL,3,CWelsh Bible printed in 1588 to go on
OL,4,Cdisplay in Wales for first time
OL,6,FThe Bible will be presented at the
OL,7,FCathedral Libraries and Collections
OL,8,FAssociation (Calca) conference at St
OL,9,FDavids on June 17, before being put on
OL,10,Fpublic display in the cathedral's
OL,11,Ftreasury between June 17 and July 9.
OL,13,FThe Rt Rev Dorrien Davies, the Bishop
OL,14,Fof St Davids, said: "I first saw the
OL,15,FBible that William Morgan gave to
OL,16,FWestminster Abbey library when I was
OL,17,Fin London for St Davids Day earlier
OL,18,Fthis year.
