OL,6,FDuring the work, Morgan stayed at
OL,7,FWestminster Abbey's deanery which was
OL,8,Fthe home of then-dean Gabriel Goodman
OL,9,F` a fellow Welshman and close friend.
OL,11,FMorgan presented the book to Goodman
OL,12,Fwith a Latin inscription, recording
OL,13,Fthat he was making a gift to the
OL,14,Flibrary.
OL,16,FTony Trowles, librarian and head of
OL,17,Fthe abbey's collection, told the PA
OL,18,Fnews agency: "It has been in our
OL,19,Flibrary ever since.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
