OL,3,CWelsh Bible printed in 1588 to go on
OL,4,Cdisplay in Wales for first time
OL,6,FHe said the printing process was
OL,7,F"highly complex and technical" with
OL,8,Feach letter arranged backwards and
OL,9,Fseveral pages printed on one sheet.
OL,11,FThe book is printed on paper and bound
OL,12,Fin leather over covers made from wood,
OL,13,Fa process used at the time.
OL,15,FThe Dean of St Davids, the Very Revd
OL,16,FDr Sarah Rowland Jones, said: "It
OL,17,Fseems fitting that its first visit to
OL,18,FWales should be here, to the home of
OL,19,Four patron saint, at our spiritual
OL,20,Fheart.
