OL,6,F"We look forward to having it on show
OL,7,Fbefore its return to the abbey, to
OL,8,Fshare with Welsh Christians of all
OL,9,Ftraditions, for whom Y Beibl Cyssegr-
OL,10,FLan of 1588 Bible is a uniquely
OL,11,Fvaluable treasure in our heritage of
OL,12,Ffaith and language."
